# name: test_mcp_tool_policy_blocks_with_gateway_footer
  '''
  JamJet demo: MCP tool policy
  
    This demo uses an MCP-shaped request envelope to show policy evaluation.
    It is not yet an MCP proxy. Full MCP proxy support is planned for JamJet Gateway.
  
    Agent:    DeterministicDemoAgent (mocked — no real model)
    MCP request:
      server: postgres-mcp
      tool:   postgres/database.delete_all_customers
  
    Policy: block tools matching '*delete*'
  
    Decision: BLOCKED  (rule: *delete*)
    Executed: false
    Audit:    <TMP>/.jamjet-demo/runs/mcp-tool-policy-001.json
  
    The model is mocked. The enforcement path is real.
  
  '''
# ---
